<span class="s0">def </span><span class="s1">gamma_correct(rgba_0_255</span><span class="s0">, </span><span class="s1">gamma):</span>
    <span class="s1">corrected = round(</span><span class="s4">255.0 </span><span class="s1">* math.pow(rgba_0_255 / </span><span class="s4">255.0</span><span class="s0">, </span><span class="s1">gamma))</span>
    <span class="s0">return </span><span class="s1">max(min(int(corrected)</span><span class="s0">, </span><span class="s4">255</span><span class="s1">)</span><span class="s0">, </span><span class="s4">0</span><span class="s1">)</span>
